Okhulumela iReaction Unit South Africa (Rusa), uMnuz Prem Berlam, uthe ngabo-7 ebusuku bafike emzini oseduze kwaseThunder Town emgwaqweni uVincent Dickson lapho omunye wabagilwa ebefuna usizo khona. “Kutholakale ukuthi abangani abathathu bebesendleleni egodukayo eya eHilltop eduze kwaseCanelands Library lapho bebone khona ukuthi bayalandelwa ngamadoda amathathu. Omunye wabasolwa uvulele ngenhlamvu izikhawu ezine ebhekise kubagilwa.” Uthe abagilwa babaleke ngokwehlukana. Uthe balaphe indoda eneminyaka engu-37 emnweni, omunye udubuleke kabili engalweni. Imbangela yalokuhlaselwa ayikaziwa. Okhulumela amaphoyisa KwaZulu-Natal, uCaptain Nqobile Gwala ukuqinisekisile ukuthi amadoda amathathu aneminyaka elinganiselwa ku-30 kade esendleni eya ekhaya. “Athathiwe ayiswa esibhedlela ukuyokwelashwa, amacala amathathu okuzama ukubulala avuliwe esiteshini samaphoyisa.”